{"tid":383030,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】尋找老豆的故事 Day104 1/9 【人中之龍6】","createTime":"2017-09-01T07:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T11:09:05.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4462cdb238cc3c891edd0ccaf92b9e91f11ca696","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=7YrFDRuc1Y%2FoZZeHiVOtiNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=89844f47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=7YrFDRuc1Y%2FoZZeHiVOtiNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=321f25b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=7YrFDRuc1Y%2FoZZeHiVOtiNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8f9880fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"f04f4e4790f3b21ba552629dd47b98c20d037d24","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79db2196c308762be7ea94cb14faace3c1e771ce","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc56d7e0ad4984939d69356c5e0944a9d392ba3","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ead18272ef54328c87b214fdd627e46f8ae47","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77fef78d0009a1aca13024cfa5a62763792c4c9","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dccdf554c1428482d09383ca35169b8b8e36c2d","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200d132888dea7ce220f3d09beedc2bd83fe9c2d","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec2d7763ba25bea227b1b224fc785312e6db6ce","tid":383030,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class